    <item>
      <title>苹果业绩预测不温不火，中国市场疲软引发担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/apple-s-tepid-forecast-china-weakness-spark-concern-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果即将进入今年最关键的销售期，这引发了人们对收入增长和竞争激烈的中国市场持续疲软的新担忧。Deepwater Asset Management 管理合伙人 Gene Munster 与 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”上进行讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/apple-s-tepid-forecast-china-weakness-spark-concern-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 19:18:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷利差前景乐观：瑞银的 Mish</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/outlook-for-credit-spreads-positive-ubs-s-mish-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银信贷策略主管 Matthew Mish 表示，红色横扫将是信贷利差的最佳结果，信贷利差的整体前景相当乐观。CreditSights 全球策略主管 Winnie Cisar 建议仔细研究选举噪音。他们就“彭博实际收益率”采访了 Sonali Basak。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/outlook-for-credit-spreads-positive-ubs-s-mish-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 19:18:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道明证券的戈德伯格：如果出现红色浪潮，预计 10 年期收益率将接近 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/expect-10-year-close-to-5-if-we-see-red-wave-goldberg-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道明证券美国利率策略主管 Gennadiy Goldberg 表示，如果特朗普获胜，共和党大获全胜，10 年期国债收益率可能最终达到 5% 左右。法国兴业银行美国利率策略主管 Subadra Rajappa 表示，如果债券收益率下跌，风险资产可能全面受到影响。他们就“彭博实际收益率”与 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/expect-10-year-close-to-5-if-we-see-red-wave-goldberg-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 19:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
